des:
Want to learn more about Heritage Church in Barrington, Lake Zurich, and Round Lake Beach, Illinois? You can ask about our locations, service times, website address--even a recent message. 

You can ask:
"Alexa, ask Heritage Church for service times"
"Alexa, ask Heritage Church for a recent message"
"Alexa, ask Heritage Church about locations"

and more.
